# Ignore everything by default
*

# Keep directories traversable so negation rules can work
!*/

# Keep this file
!.gitignore

# Executable/source files to keep in git
!*.ipynb
!*.py
!*.ps1
!*.bat
!*.cmd
!*.sh

# Project metadata/docs often needed to run or reproduce
!README*
!*.md
!requirements*.txt
!pyproject.toml
!setup.py
!environment.yml
!Pipfile
!Pipfile.lock
